        {
            "title": "伊朗緊張局勢施壓黃金及其他金屬,美國礦業股大跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/RRT_xg1M9RiRqWuUwZgKag--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA7H00D_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 美國礦業股週一下跌,此前黃金和白銀價格因荷莫茲海峽關閉引發的通脹擔憂而暴跌,原油價格則大幅上漲。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">南方銅業、紐蒙特黃金、阿格尼科鷹礦業和惠頓貴金屬的股價分別下跌1.9%至2.7%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">黃金價格週一跌至一週低點,隨後小幅回升,原因是伊朗威脅要對美國接管一艘伊朗貨船進行報復,推動美元和油價走高。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">週一,在接管該貨船後,美國與伊朗之間的停火協議似乎岌岌可危。由於擔心停火協議破裂以及荷莫茲海峽的航運將繼續大部分停滯,油價上漲約5%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-6e4706a5-af84-3dba-bc90-f3a4fdee13ce-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國總統唐納德·川普週日晚間表示,美國對一艘試圖繞過封鎖的伊朗船隻開火並將其俘獲,雙方還聲稱對方違反了停火協議。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普表示,美國特使正前往巴基斯坦進行更多停火談判。但伊朗媒體報導稱,德黑蘭尚未承諾參加任何未來的談判。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">油價週一飆升高達7%,使市場對伊朗戰爭的通脹影響保持高度警惕。自2月下旬衝突開始以來,對能源推動通脹的擔憂一直是金屬價格的主要拖累因素。市場預期全球央行將通過加息來應對這些價格壓力,這對黃金等無收益資產而言並非好兆頭。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"> </p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E7%B7%8A%E5%BC%B5%E5%B1%80%E5%8B%A2%E6%96%BD%E5%A3%93%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E9%87%91%E5%B1%AC-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%A4%A6%E6%A5%AD%E8%82%A1%E5%A4%A7%E8%B7%8C-182107220.html",
