        {
            "title": "日本地震後解除海嘯警報 未報告任何損失",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"US Geological Survey\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"735\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/C4izNdjLOLQ54A.h32RpiA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTczNQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/1bf815f1c233d66b4dc9f9792989c60e\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">US Geological Survey</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 日本公共廣播機構NHK報導稱，日本東北海岸附近周一發生強烈地震，在久慈港引發約80釐米海嘯，其他地區也出現較小海浪。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">內閣官房長官木原稔對記者表示，目前尚無損失或人員傷亡報告。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日本氣象廳隨後解除此前對青森縣以及北海道部分地區發布的海嘯警報和注意報。這些地區觀測到的海嘯高度僅為數十釐米，程度較輕，通常不太可能造成破壞。不過，NHK仍呼籲受影響地區民眾遠離海岸和河岸，以防隨後可能出現更大的海嘯。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-406308f7-2ece-3364-be82-939e25e745ac-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據美國地質調查局數據，這次地震發生在當地時間下午4:50後不久，震中位於日本東北沿海，震級初步估計為7.4級。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日本氣象廳稱，震源深度估計約為10公里，遠在數百公里外的東京建築也出現搖晃。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"735\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/FFqLhOfIFERBAwcssRwDyw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTczNQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/b4cbdb54f24d065546398e55b245f2d4\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日本首相高市早苗表示，政府正在設立緊急響應中心，並呼籲地震影響地區民眾前往安全地點避險。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">東京電力公司表示，正在調查地震對其設施的影響；北海道電力稱，其火電及核電站尚未確認任何異常；東北電力則表示，其核電和火電設施未檢測到異常。NHK稱，此次地震導致岩手縣新幹線列車停運。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Japan Lifts Tsunami Warnings After Quake, No Damage Reported</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Chris Gallagher.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
